data.description:
Bayside Lakes - Heated private pool - 5 Bedrooms - 3 Bathrooms - Preserve View - There are so many features to  love about this home.  The large primary bedroom is upstairs as well as 3 other bedrooms.  1 Bedroom and Full Bath is downstairs.  The kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless updated appliances, lots of cabinet space and large island.   The bones are great with a 
2021 roof,  Generac Generator, Solar Panels and Hurricane Shutters.
